The Utilities repositories contains scripts and applications that are short and hopeful useful.

Website Check
websitecheck.pl
This utility runs as a service on the Linux/Unix server and pings a URL and will send an email if an error occurs

Delicious Bad Bookmark Checker
delicious_bb_check.py
Uses the Delicious API to pull a list of the user's bookmarks and the tests the links to see if they are still valid prints out the invalid list.  
